{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_grfisfitzfljf7bw3ljw6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"108675980","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-20T20-12-48-884Z/baseline-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a `Map` for key-value storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance with standard cache operations.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key. Returns `undefined` if the key does not exist.\n\n```javascript\nconst value = cache.get('key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache for the given key. Returns the stored value.\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('key', 'value')\nconst storedValue = cache.set('key', 'value')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves an entry from the cache by key. Returns `true` if the value was removed, `false` otherwise.\n\n```javascript\nconst wasDeleted = cache.delete('key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4770,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":4670},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f8585206-7c46-4bf8-9381-75ab765affa3","uuid":"05469054-4dc6-496c-a29c-ade023c06929","timestamp":"2026-07-21T01:27:18.380Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"108675980","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-20T20-12-48-884Z/baseline-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f8585206-7c46-4bf8-9381-75ab765affa3","uuid":"196bc3e8-f4f1-48fd-b355-64d4fc0126b2","timestamp":"2026-07-21T01:27:18.390Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-20T20-12-48-884Z/baseline-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a `Map` for key-value storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance with standard cache operations.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key. Returns `undefined` if the key does not exist.\n\n```javascript\nconst value = cache.get('key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache for the given key. Returns the stored value.\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('key', 'value')\nconst storedValue = cache.set('key', 'value')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves an entry from the cache by key. Returns `true` if the value was removed, `false` otherwise.\n\n```javascript\nconst wasDeleted = cache.delete('key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
